quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nun, nditsuba khukalamu nende kabahandikanga"
  68,2,Ewe khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo sholi omulalu tawe
  68,3,Netoto bwene oli nomurungo omukhongo kulaliwa tawe
  68,4,Netoto bwene oli nende ebima ebilayi
  68,5,Hambi ano olalola nabo bosi nibalole
  68,6,Ni wina mwinywe womurwe omubii
  68,7,"Toto bwene Nyasaye wuwo niye umanyile muno ulia wakora okhurula khunjila yiyie, ne amanyile muno ulia ulikhubulunjifu"
  68,8,Olaloonda balia abamainji tawe
  68,9,Bekombanga mbu wakhatoratosiyekhwo nabo bakhutoratosilia
  68,10,Ne olaloonda buli ulia witsubanga muno Oweshileka Omutswatswani tawe
  68,11,Uyiyayiyanga natswatswania
  68,12,"Umwikalili wamalayi, Owetsimbi Omwonooni"
  68,13,"Womwoyo omwangaranu, khulwa ako nomwonooni wamanyikhana khutsimbi"
  68,14,"Khulwokhubeela, ali nende emiandu nende Abana"
  68,15,"Nibasomelwa amahandiko kefu nibaboola mbu: “etso nit’singano tsiabakhale.”"
  68,16,Khulamurakhwo eshimanyisio khuliulu lilie
  68,17,"Netoto bwene khulabatema , shinga khwatema Abandu bomukunda, olwabetsuba mbu balauna okhuchesa obulachweya"
  68,18,"Ne nibalaboola mbu: “ Nyasaye nachama” tawe"
  68,19,"Awo, eshikhole shiamaraba, okhurula khu Nyasaye nishikholekha khumukunda oko nabo nibali mutsindoolo"
  68,20,Nikuba neshiilima eshikhongo
  68,21,Nibalaangana mumabwibwi nibushiele
  68,22,Tsie mumukunda kwenyu nimuli toto mbu mutsitsanga okhuchesa
  68,23,"Ne nibarula\tnibasungana mubwimoonyo"
  68,24,Mbu abulaho Omumanani yesi- yesi ulenjila mumukunda olwa lelo
  68,25,Ne nibarula mumabwibwi nibasuubile
  68,26,"Olwa bakulola baboola mbu,: “toto bwene khukorere.”"
  68,27,Halali efwe khwimilwe
  68,28,"Omulayi mubo naboola mbu: “shebaboolelekhwo,\tkhulwashina mularetsanga Nyasaye mumioyo chenyu ?”"
  68,29,"Nibaboola mbu : “ niwoluyali Nyasaye wefu toto efwe khuli abonooni “"
  68,30,Nibakalukhana abeene khubeene okhufunanania
  68,31,"Nibaboola mbu: “abaane efwe! khuruumile eshichelo”"
  68,32,"Awundi Nyasaye wefu alakhuwa amalayi okhushila kano, efwe khukalushila Nyasaye wefu"
  68,33,"Endio nilweshinyasio shili, ne eshinyasio sheyindukho neshikhongo muno, bamangakhwo bayie"
  68,34,Toto bwene balia abaria Nyasaye wabu baliba nende emikunda chobwokholo
  68,35,"Ne, khwakhakhola abasalamu shinga aboononi"
  68,36,Mukhabeele murie? mubusinjia murie
  68,37,"Nohomba\tmulineshitabu shiamusomanga mwo"
  68,38,Mbu mulanyoolamwo akamwayanza
  68,39,"Nohomba muli nebitsubo khwifwe, ebiliboosia khu inyanga yeyindukho, mbu toto bwene mulinyoola koosi pe kamubusinjia"
  68,40,"Barebe mbu: “ni wina mubo Omwimilisi wakano"
  68,41,Nohomba bali nende abasaanji ? mana babarere nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto
  68,42,"Inyanga lwomuluku kulifunulwa, nebalilangwa okhwinamila Nyasaye, neshibalinyalilwa tawe"
  68,43,"Tsimoni tsiabu tsilihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibalia toto bwene balaangungwa okhwinamila Nyasaye ( nibali khushialo) nibali abalamu"
  68,44,"Ndeshela balia bafukula likhuwa lino, khulabasitilia eshinyasio kalahakalaha munjila yabalamanyile tawe"
  68,45,"Ne ndalabahelesia ebise, amaraba kanje ni amasiro"
  68,46,Nohomba ebasabanga omurungo nabo bashilungwa eshichelo esho
  68,47,Nohoma bali nende kefisa kabahandikanga
  68,48,"Linda shinga Nyasaye wuwo yetsa okhubusia, ne olaba shinga omundu weyimonye, olwayalaanga nafwinyiikhe"
  68,49,"Tsikhanyanga okhumuulila tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwe, yakhasalilwe khulukuku nafunanibwa"
  68,50,"Halali Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namwawula , namukhola okhuba mubandu abalayi"
  68,51,"Ne abakhayi hambi hatiti bakhukwisie khulwe tsimoni tsiabu, olwabawulilanga ametsulisio ka-Nyasaye. Nibaboolanga mbu: “ toto bwene ye ni omulalu.”"
  68,52,Ne amakhuwa kano (Ikurani) shikali halali ni ametsulisio khubiloonje bioosi